COMMAND: NovaGPT

HOW TO USE:
enter NovaGPT          # Enter chat mode
Nova@"question"        # Ask NovaGPT something
exit                   # Return to main prompt

EXAMPLE:
enter NovaGPT
NovaGPT=> Nova@"How do I create a variable?"
NovaGPT=> Nova@"What is NovaScript?"
NovaGPT=> exit

DESCRIPTION:
NovaGPT is a simulated AI assistant integrated into NovaHub. It provides
guidance on NovaScript syntax, NovaHub commands, and development questions.
Currently simulated with pattern-based responses. Future versions may
support real LLM integration.

LANGUAGE:
System

